id, \u201cWhat should I say?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cSay, 'He is Allah, the One,' (112:1) and the two chapters of refuge, al-Falaq and al-Nas, every evening and morning three times. They will be\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28156,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/26\/salat-al-witr-ahl-quran\/","url_meta":{"origin":34802,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Nawafil: Witr prayer recommended, not obligation","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 26, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ali ibn Abi Talib reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah is numerically odd and He loves what is odd, so perform the Witr prayer, O people of the Quran!\u201d Ali ibn Abi Talib, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cThe Witr\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2696,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/03\/31\/quran-sunnah-then-ijtihad\/","url_meta":{"origin":34802,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Ijtihad: Judge with the Quran, Sunnah, then your opinion","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 31, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Harith ibn 'Amr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, sent Mu\u2019adh to Yemen and he said, \u201cHow will you judge?\u201d Mu\u2019adh said, \u201cI will judge according to the Book of Allah.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cWhat if it is not in the Book of Allah?\u201d Mu\u2019adh\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35276,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/02\/20\/special-place-jahannam\/","url_meta":{"origin":34802,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Ostentation: Special place in Hell for reciters showing off","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 20, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cSeek refuge in Allah from the pit of sorrow.\u201d They said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, what is the pit of sorrow?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cIt is a valley in Hell from which Hell itself seeks refuge\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35499,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/04\/01\/angel-waiting\/","url_meta":{"origin":34802,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Judgment: Angel of Horn waiting to start Resurrection","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 1, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id al-Khudri reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cHow can I be comfortable while the holder of the trumpet is holding it to his lips, his head lowered and waiting for the order to blow it?\u201d The Muslims said, \u201cWhat should we say,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37533,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/12\/15\/sunnah-like-quran\/","url_meta":{"origin":34802,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Sunnah: The Prophet\u2019s commands are like Allah\u2019s commands","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 15, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Miqdam ibn Ma\u2019dikarib reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, what the Messenger of Allah has forbidden is like what Allah has forbidden.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2664 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u200c\u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u0650\u0642\u0652\u062f\u064e\u0627\u0645\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0645\u064e\u0639\u0652\u062f\u0650\u064a\u0643\u064e\u0631\u0650\u0628\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/34802","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.c